{"place_id": "rebirth", "place_name": "Rebirth", "source_url": "https://www.google.com/maps/place/Rebirth/@25.0213738,121.5303775,17z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0x3442a988e919f47d:0xc36d3628b077d501!8m2!3d25.021369!4d121.5329524!9m1!1b1!16s%2Fg%2F1ptvr89ww?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI2MDMxMS4wIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D", "reviewer_name": "Chipin Chen", "review_text": "彷彿走進老闆客廳一樣的親切感,每個角落都藏有小故事,堆積如山的漫畫書據說都是別人給的,是低聲聊天或是好好拿一本書來讀都超級棒的空間 空間已經滿分了,老闆的餐也很有趣,菜單名真的讓人很猜不透哈哈,這次點的是麻婆豆腐,好好吃啊,不過驚艷的是小菜的生魚片!咖啡廳的生魚片這麼好吃真的很厲害,好喜歡!!不過要1800左右才會供餐,還有就是份量超大,一個人吃竟然有點吃力 更多", "star_rating": 5.0, "review_date_text": "1 年前", "owner_response_text": null, "owner_response_date": null, "scraped_at": "2026-03-17T17:05:34.056152+00:00", "review_unique_key": "d71d6ddae88ffcb330a5a39a5e6be32a71d1cc0ebe13cd508f8b8ade2966ab43", "review_date_estimated": null, "scrape_run_id": "20260317T165520Z", "review_language": null, "reviewer_profile_url": null, "likes_count": null, "raw_review_metadata": {"review_id": "ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNmNjlUaFp3EAE", "relative_date_text": "1 年前", "google_place_token": "0x3442a988e919f47d-0xc36d3628b077d501"}}
